### 5. Teste negativo: atendimento ja vinculado a outro prontuario
POST {{baseUrl}}/prontuario
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "empresaId": "{{empresaId}}",
  "filialId": "{{filialId}}",
  "atendimentoId": "{{atendimentoId}}",
  "pacienteId": "{{pacientePessoaId}}"
}

### 6. Deletar prontuario
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/prontuario/{{prontuarioId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
